msgid "data/text_misc.xml.append$//text[@name=\"tip_bomb_flak\"]"
msgstr ""
"Bomb flaks function similarly to standard flaks, but do double system damage"
" and cost a missile to fire. They are great for taking down systems, but "
"don't pierce shields like other ballistic weapons."

